name: activateABankAccount

testSteps.description: Given that im logged into manage bank account page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Supplier Management,Manage Bank Account}

testSteps.description: Then the manage bank account page and its contents should show up
When i deactivate the first bank account if its active
Then the the first supplier bank account should be expired
When i click on activate button of the first supplier bank account
Then the bank account validated successfully notification should show up
Then the the first supplier bank account should not be expired

title: Activate a bank account
